$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Nexys A7 out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Seven-seg: decoded readout — counter / accelerometer axes (all digits live). Buttons: staggered presses.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! led0 $end
$var wire 1 " led1 $end
$var wire 1 # led2 $end
$var wire 1 $ led3 $end
$var wire 1 % led4 $end
$var wire 1 & led5 $end
$var wire 1 ' led6 $end
$var wire 1 ( led7 $end
$var wire 1 ) led8 $end
$var wire 1 * led9 $end
$var wire 1 + led10 $end
$var wire 1 , led11 $end
$var wire 1 - led12 $end
$var wire 1 . led13 $end
$var wire 1 / led14 $end
$var wire 1 0 led15 $end
$var wire 1 1 sw0 $end
$var wire 1 2 sw1 $end
$var wire 1 3 sw2 $end
$var wire 1 4 sw3 $end
$var wire 1 5 sw4 $end
$var wire 1 6 sw5 $end
$var wire 1 7 sw6 $end
$var wire 1 8 sw7 $end
$var wire 1 9 sw8 $end
$var wire 1 : sw9 $end
$var wire 1 ; sw10 $end
$var wire 1 < sw11 $end
$var wire 1 = sw12 $end
$var wire 1 > sw13 $end
$var wire 1 ? sw14 $end
$var wire 1 @ sw15 $end
$var wire 1 A btnC $end
$var wire 1 B btnU $end
$var wire 1 C btnL $end
$var wire 1 D btnR $end
$var wire 1 E btnD $end
$var wire 4 F digit0 $end
$var wire 4 G digit1 $end
$var wire 4 H digit2 $end
$var wire 4 I digit3 $end
$var wire 4 J digit4 $end
$var wire 4 K digit5 $end
$var wire 4 L digit6 $end
$var wire 4 M digit7 $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
